commit.message:
Add ArchivedClassesTest to compare archived serialized classes against
the serialized current classes.
The archived classes were built against version: 25.0.1+8-LTS-27
The test will fail if the archived serialized classes are missing from the REPO
or if there are any changes to the serialized bytes.
List any classes in the current runtime that are not in the archive.
The change of ByteOrder from a class to enum is reported as an approved incompatible change.
